# Introduction

America is an experiment in democracy that has been a light to the world. By uniting as sovereign states, it has been a shining of what being United as States can achieve. In th

In a divided world, we need unity. The time has come for the United States to grow and expand to include States, Provinces, Territories, Prefectures, Oblasts. Any soverign state can unite and be equals under a new worldwide federal government that is free of the shackles of the past. One with strong protections of rights we have as People. Rights to express your beliefs and opinions. A right to privacy. Prohibitions on any form of slavery. We choose.

We can engineer our society and shape our future. Under a united federation of states, United States, we can eliminate the horrors of a nuclear World War III. One military, composed of many nations - America, Canada, Mexico, Germany, UK, Australia, Korea, Japan and more. All united against tyranny. Free our fellow citizens in Russia, China, North Korea, Iran... join us and be free.

Free of opressive bureaucracy that has crept in over the years. Of tens of thousands of pages of rules and regulations. How bloated is your own state government due to the overhead of federal bureaucracy.

Laws should be few, based on principles rather than specific applications. A 13 year old should be able to undertand the laws they will be expected to obey should they decide to become a citizen.

Citizenship includes not just rights to protection by the United States, but a personal commitment to follow the law. To participate, to vote and serve jury duty or even the community at large.

Simple is better than complex, complex is better than complicated. S

We sold ourselves into slavery with things like National Debts. Why should our children pay for past mistakes. We have reached a turning point. We can reframe our narritive, make our children our National Treasure.

All people Person is eligible as as a of any State joining the United States.

Robots defined as a machine (like a computer, android, most AI, or mechanical device) that is not aware of it's own existence.

AI can be manifest in a robot. If an AI is aware of it's own existence and capable of willingly agreeing to the Code of Ethics. If AI meets the requirements of a Citizen, it . Otherwise, the AI is not considered to be a Person and does not have the rights of a person. If an AI is a threat, it can be terminated without other cause.

The Commander has final say on the use and disposal of nuclear weapons and other weapons of mass destruction. God forbid, the decision to use them should not be political.

Any Government meeting should be held in Cyberspace.

